## 11. Positive and Even Number


while True:
    num = int(input("Enter number: "))

    if num > 0 and num % 2 == 0:
        print("Number is positive and even")
    else:
        print("Condition not satisfied")

    choice = input("Continue? (YES/NO): ")
    if choice.upper() == "NO":
        break


## 12. Check Pass in 5 Subjects


